cff-version: "1.2.0"

message: >-
  If you use Quantiles, please cite it as below.

title: "Quantiles: Local-first AI evaluation infrastructure"

abstract: >-
  Quantiles is an agent-native CLI and SDKs for local-first AI evaluation workflows,
  helping teams run benchmarks and evaluations, inspect sample-level outputs, and
  compare eval runs.

type: software

authors:
  - name: "Quantiles Contributors"

repository-code: "https://github.com/quantiles-evals/quantiles"

url: "https://quantiles.io"

license: Apache-2.0

keywords:
  - "AI evaluation"
  - "AI benchmarking"
  - "evaluation infrastructure"
  - "LLM evaluation"
  - "agent evaluation"
